rows.label: qst703205_msg0001
rows.name: What happened?

rows.label: qst703205_msg0002
rows.name: Did you get injured somewhere...?

rows.label: qst703205_msg0003
rows.name:
I did it! I flipping did it!
I finally whooped a monster's butt!

rows.label: qst703205_msg0004
rows.name: Rita, please calm down.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0005
rows.name:
You said "finally"... What exactly
have you been doing before?

rows.label: qst703205_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh, she's been skillfully avoiding them.
This is her first official victory.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0007
rows.name:
Hey, Kaede-chan!
Do I look buff now or what?

rows.label: qst703205_msg0008
rows.name:
After beating one monster?
Just listen to yourself.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0009
rows.name:
And even then, it looks like the poor
guy might have just tripped and fallen
onto your weapon...

rows.label: qst703205_msg0010
rows.name: Ugh... So I'm useless after all, then...

rows.label: qst703205_msg0011
rows.name: ...Rita, take a look at that.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0012
rows.name:
Whoa!
Is that...Lasqam Cove?

rows.label: qst703205_msg0013
rows.name:
It's a huge natural harbor, as you
remember. And yet, looking at it
from here, it appears tiny.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0014
rows.name:
Don't focus so much on your strength,
but just look at how far we've come.
I'm proud of you for that.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0015
rows.name: K-Kaede-chan~~!

rows.label: qst703205_msg0016
rows.name:
What's that face you're pulling?
Seriously...

rows.label: qst703205_msg0017
rows.name:
Seriously. All this noise about
a simple exploration mission.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0018
rows.name:
Everybody starts somewhere.
Thinking back to when we met them,
isn't this success enough?

rows.label: qst703205_msg0019
rows.name:
I believe Rita may yet grow into
a fine Driver indeed.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0020
rows.name:
It's not every day that Shin offer
praise like that, is it?

rows.label: qst703205_msg0021
rows.name:
That pretty much settles it.
She'll do great things one day.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0022
rows.name:
...Everyone.
Thank you for all your assistance.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0023
rows.name:
After we've gone around Gula,
I think we'll find some other place
to explore.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0024
rows.name:
Then we might meet again somewhere, 
mightn't we?

rows.label: qst703205_msg0025
rows.name:
Very good! On that day, it may be you
helping us out.

rows.label: qst703205_msg0026
rows.name: Ohhh... Don't make fun of me!

rows.label: qst703205_msg0027
rows.name:
I don't think he is! Anyway, I'm looking
forward to that day. We'll be cheering
you on, you two.
